title: ~Owner occupied from 2013-2019 and well maintained ~
posting_body: One of the best condo locations in West Campus-very close to UT and Guadalupe St ~Excellent roommate plan with 2 full baths and 2 generous size bedrooms on opposite sides of the condo; ~Both bedrooms have room for a bed and a desk; both have large walk in closets ~2 entrances to the condo and 2 reserved parking spaces in the garage ~Many improvements including recent HVAC, water heater, attic insulation and interior paint-see attachments for list ~Granite in kitchen and both baths, laminate and tile flooring throughout-no carpet ~Refrigerator, washer and dryer included ~Reasonable HOA dues cover water, trash, sewer in addition to exterior maintenance, common area maintenance, pool, etc....~
